Hey there! You are running SDK 5.5.0.GA with CLI 7.0.2 and have SDK 7.0.2.GA set as teh default:
{code} 
[INFO]  tiapp.xml <sdk-version> set to 5.5.1.GA, but current Titanium SDK set to 7.0.2.GA
{code}
Reading the logs, you are also running on Xcode 9.2 which is not compatible with SDK 5.x. Xcode 9 was releases last September and requird some CLI changes that are present in SDK 6.3+, so please either use 5.5.1.GA for your config (appc ti setup sdk -> Select 5.5.1.GA) and downgrade your Xcode to 8.x or (highly recommended) update your project to 7.0.2.GA for full compatibility with latest tooling and CLI. 

You can find older Xcode versions [here|https://stackoverflow.com/a/10335943/5537752], I hope that helps!
